<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <title>Home - Brand</title>
    {{>links}}
</head>

<body>
{{>navigation}}

    <main class="page landing-page">
        <section class="clean-block clean-hero" style="background-image:url(&quot;assets/img/tech/image4.jpg&quot;);color:rgba(9, 162, 255, 0.85);">
            <div class="text">
                <h2>Don't wait, ask your questions now!</h2>
                <p>Be part of the presentation, write down youre toughts and get instant feedback from the host!<br> Ask, Vote, Talk</p><a href='/chat'><button class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg" type="button">Try Now</button></a></div>
        </section>
        <section class="clean-block clean-info dark">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="block-heading">
                    <h2 class="text-info">Info</h2>
                    <p>An easy way to engage with the host and the public. Now you can ask everything and the hosts will see your question in real time. No need to wait!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-md-6"><img class="img-thumbnail" src="assets/img/scenery/image5.jpg"></div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h3>Be part of everything</h3>
                        <div class="getting-started-info">
                            <p>Special chat rooms are assigned to each presentation, you can get feedback from the audience and even save the questions to respond to them later.</p>
                        </div><button class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg" type="button">Join Now</button></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="clean-block features">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="block-heading">
                    <h2 class="text-info">Features</h2>
                    <p>It has been never this easy to interract with the public, the platform offers a clean design and intuitive mechanics to make everything just easy.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="row justify-content-center">
                    <div class="col-md-5 feature-box"><i class="icon-star icon"></i>
                        <h4>Bootstrap 4</h4>
                        <p>Clean and powerfull bootstrap library designed for a great look.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-5 feature-box"><i class="icon-pencil icon"></i>
                        <h4>Customizable</h4>
                        <p>Pick your own chat rooms you want to make part of. Ask your questions and interract with everybody.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-5 feature-box"><i class="icon-screen-smartphone icon"></i>
                        <h4>Responsive</h4>
                        <p>Dosen't matter what device you use, the responsive design will make the website look natural.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-5 feature-box"><i class="icon-refresh icon"></i>
                        <h4>Real Time</h4>
                        <p>Instant messaging app that provides real time data, you don't have to wait or even raise your hand!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="clean-block about-us">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="block-heading">
                    <h2 class="text-info">About Me</h2>
                    <p>Firs year student at AUAS. Made this project to make the presentations more entertaining.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="row justify-content-center">
                    <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                        <div class="card clean-card text-center"><img class="card-img-top w-100 d-block" src="assets/img/avatars/avatar1.jpg">
                            <div class="card-body info">
                                <h4 class="card-title">Zamfir Cristian</h4>
                                <p class="card-text">Creative, Fun, Energic</p>
                                <div class="icons"><a href="#"><i class="icon-social-facebook"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-social-instagram"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-social-twitter"></i></a></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    {{>footer}}
    {{>scripts}}

</body>

</html>